
 Games::Sudoku::Pdf - Produce pdf files from your digital Sudoku sources or collections. 

 An easy way to create pdf files of 9x9 Sudoku puzzles from your input.
 Sixteen variants of 9x9 Sudoku are supported. (See the output of scripts/example.pl.)
 Specify the page format and puzzle arrangement (columns x rows) per page 
 while the positioning and scaling is done automatically.
 A command line script is available for convenience.

 Steffen Heinrich, Feb. 2024
